{
  "id": "6652c5ec302a5d001c0bdbb8",
  "title": "捏造",
  "created": 1716700658,
  "updated": 1716762713,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6652c5ec302a5d001c0bdbb8",
      "text": "捏造",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716700658,
      "updated": 1716700658
    },
    {
      "id": "6652c5f2aff09e000040ff0a",
      "text": "捏造は本来「ねつぞう」ではなく「でつぞう」だ、という主張は誤りであり「でっちあげ」が「捏上げ」であるという説もでっちあげ、という主張",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716700658,
      "updated": 1716700713
    },
    {
      "id": "6652c629aff09e000040ff0c",
      "text": "https://x.com/amane_murakumo/status/1794250491893014807?s=46&t=gkSZtjGEtUZPO0JCzBxCBw",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716700713,
      "updated": 1716700716
    },
    {
      "id": "6652c62caff09e000040ff0d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716700716,
      "updated": 1716700716
    },
    {
      "id": "6652c62caff09e000040ff0e",
      "text": "面白くなってきたぞ()[nishio.icon][bsahd.icon]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1716700717,
      "updated": 1716704488
    },
    {
      "id": "6652c5f5aff09e000040ff0b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716700662,
      "updated": 1716700662
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3baff09e00005b9ecf",
      "text": ">[amane_murakumo https://x.com/amane_murakumo/status/1794250491893014807] 実は正しくは「でつぞう」であるって言うのも「詳細に言うと正確じゃない」と考えられる点がある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742973,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9ed0",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9ed1",
      "text": "> と言うのは辞典参照しても「デツ〜」が元来の読み方で「ネツ〜」は慣用音と書いてあり、",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9ed2",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9ed3",
      "text": "> サイトによっては古い音はデツと書いてあるんだが...(リプライへ続く)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9ed4",
      "text": "> >a110ami: 「捏造」が正しくは「でつぞう」なの知らなくて本で見かけたときに「ルビが誤字ってる……」と思いながら一応ググってみた事ある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9ed5",
      "text": "> 「誤字とか言ってすみませんでした」の気持ちと「でつぞう、言いづらすぎる　だから滅びた」の気持ちが発生した",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9ed6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9ed7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9ed8",
      "text": ">[amane_murakumo https://x.com/amane_murakumo/status/1794250497127575950] (承前)漢字字典参照してみると、",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9ed9",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9eda",
      "text": "> 「呉音」がネツ、ネチで「漢音」がデツとある。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9edb",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9edc",
      "text": "> で日本における漢字音のうち早くに伝わったのは「呉音」の方である。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9edd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9ede",
      "text": ">[amane_murakumo https://x.com/amane_murakumo/status/1794250504975040837] その上、",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9edf",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9ee0",
      "text": "> 捏の音符は涅槃などにも使う涅(ネツ)で基本的に頭音はn、ナ行である。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9ee1",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9ee2",
      "text": "> 実際、再構された上古音は*niːɡ(ニー〔グ〕)で、中古音もnet(ネッ)だ。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9ee3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9ee4",
      "text": ">[amane_murakumo https://x.com/amane_murakumo/status/1794250515255369976] おまけに言うと現行の中国語の普通話、諸方言でも基本的には「n」が頭音、",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9ee5",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9ee6",
      "text": "> 韓国語読みだとナルで、ヴェトナム語読みでもナットとかニェットと読む。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9ee7",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9ee8",
      "text": "> つまり音韻から言えば「デツ」の方が非一般的な読み方であると言える。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9ee9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9eea",
      "text": ">[amane_murakumo https://x.com/amane_murakumo/status/1794250520103878669] あともう一つ。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9eeb",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9eec",
      "text": "> でっち上げは捏ち上げが語源だと言う説だが...",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9eed",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9eee",
      "text": ">[amane_murakumo https://x.com/amane_murakumo/status/1794250530329604385] 確かに芥川龍之介などもこの字の宛て方で",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9eef",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9ef0",
      "text": "> 「捏ち上げ」などと書いており近代文学にこの用字がない訳ではない。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9ef1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9ef2",
      "text": ">[amane_murakumo https://x.com/amane_murakumo/status/1794250537476726891] ただ昨今「捏」を動詞化して活用したのが「捏ち」だと書いているサイトもあるが、",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9ef3",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9ef4",
      "text": "> 捏(でつ)つなんて動詞「無い」ぞ？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9ef5",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9ef6",
      "text": "> 捏(でつ)す　とか　捏(でつ)たり",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9ef7",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9ef8",
      "text": "> なんてのも無い。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9ef9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9efa",
      "text": ">[amane_murakumo https://x.com/amane_murakumo/status/1794250544825127025] 或いは捏上げ(でつあげ)の強調と書いてあるサイトもあるが",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9efb",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9efc",
      "text": "> 前半だけ看護を音読みで残し重箱踏",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9efd",
      "text": "> 読み風に読む必然性が無い。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9efe",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9eff",
      "text": ">[amane_murakumo https://x.com/amane_murakumo/status/1794250552404246640] よって私見ではでっち上げの語源が捏ち上げ説も非常に怪しいものだと考える。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9f00",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9f01",
      "text": ">[amane_murakumo https://x.com/amane_murakumo/status/1794251187602305048] それこそデツが正音でネツが慣用音だと言う説の方が「でっち上げ」で辞書に書かれた古い説がネット上で吹聴されているだけでは無いか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b3caff09e00005b9f02",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1716742974,
      "updated": 1716742974
    },
    {
      "id": "66536b83aff09e00005b9f0f",
      "text": "捏はつくねる、つくねと読んだ例があるとのこと（日国、15cの[倭玉篇]）[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716743045,
      "updated": 1716761267
    },
    {
      "id": "6653b3425e90c00000e26534",
      "text": " こねるの例もある",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716761412,
      "updated": 1716761413
    },
    {
      "id": "6653b28b5e90c00000e26533",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1716761226,
      "updated": 1716761226
    },
    {
      "id": "6653b83171b3c20000c3ec65",
      "text": "どうでもいい[bsahd.icon]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1716762673,
      "updated": 1716762683
    },
    {
      "id": "6653b83171b3c20000c3ec66",
      "text": "\t等幅を「とうはば」と読むか「とうふく」と読むかくらい",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1716762673,
      "updated": 1716762713
    },
    {
      "id": "6653b84271b3c20000c3ec68",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1716762690,
      "updated": 1716762690
    }
  ]
}